0 REBIRTH REMORT~
Another remort option is rebirth. In rebirth you are reset to level 2 yet
retain your skills and spells as well as stats like str/int/wis/dex/con.
Your hit points will be reset to 40, mana to 200 and move to 200. The 
advantage to rebirth is you retain all skills you at one time know and can
now gain the ones you do not. Your skills also remain trained at the same
level they were IE: If i knew magic missle at 93% then when i rebirth i
will still have magic missle at 93%. You will also be allowed to carry
an extra 50 items and 100 lbs.

Rebirth is only available at level 101 or above.
It is irriversable!
~

